/*Making a grilled cheese sammy */

// Get skillet 
// gather materials (bread, butter, cheese and any other fixins)
// Turn on burner to medium and place skillet
//add cooking spray
//Take two slices of bread and use knife to spread butter on one side of each
// Place 1 piece buttered side down in skillet
// place cheese on top
// place other piece butter side up over the other slice of  bread
// once bottom is browned flip over 
//brown the other side 
// remove from heat and place on plate
// time to eat!
